Package: ValiDatHOT
Type: Package
Title: ValiDatHOT - Package to Validate Holdout Tasks in Conjoint Analysis & MaxDiff
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joshua", "Schramm", email = "test@123.com", role = "cre"),
    person("Felix Josua", "Lang", email = "test@1235.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Marcel", "Lichters", email = "test@123.com", role = "aut"))
Description: ValiDatHOT is a package that validates Holdout tasks (HOTs) in (adaptive) Conjoint analysis as well as MaxDiff. You define the Holdout task and afterward, choose different validation metrics. ValiDatHOT is a user-friendly tool to help you test the predictive validity of your data.
BugReports: https://github.com/JoshSchramm94/ValiDatHOT/issues
